<i>I would love to be like you</i>

01:23:05.994 --> 01:23:07.928
- Are we here yet?
- No.

01:23:07.996 --> 01:23:10.396
- Now?
- We got a couple hours to go.

01:23:10.465 --> 01:23:12.592
- Now?
- Soak it up.

01:23:12.668 --> 01:23:14.727
- Now? Are we here yet?
- Must be near it.

01:23:14.803 --> 01:23:17.169
Are we getting hot or cold?

01:23:17.239 --> 01:23:19.571
- Why are we turning into here?
- We're living here.

01:23:19.641 --> 01:23:24.374
- Whoa!
- I want a moment of silence just to take this in.

01:23:24.446 --> 01:23:28.940
Okay? Before the pandemonium.
Look at this.

01:23:29.017 --> 01:23:32.680
- Here we go.
- Come on. We're here.

01:23:39.761 --> 01:23:43.925
Marley! Marley, no!
Marley! Marley! Marley!

01:23:43.999 --> 01:23:46.331
- Oh, nice.
- And we're home.

01:23:53.108 --> 01:23:56.509
Hey, Andy Rooney, if you're knocking off soon,
I'll walk with you to the train.

01:23:56.578 --> 01:24:00.207
Okay, I'm ready.
Put an exclamation point here.

